{"query_name":"04-places-heritage","query_signature":"7be580a81dee8bdaca4a14eeebb76c367d2dc1ae","tile_path":"152","payload":{"version":0.6,"generator":"Overpass API 0.7.62.11 87bfad18","osm3s":{"timestamp_osm_base":"2026-07-14T21:56:45Z","copyright":"The data included in this document is from www.openstreetmap.org. The data is made available under ODbL."},"elements":[{"type":"node","id":2190443164,"lat":52.1151467,"lon":6.5254901,"tags":{"historic":"memorial","name":"Voormalige Joodse Begraafplaats"}},{"type":"node","id":5280090987,"lat":52.1124072,"lon":6.5172529,"tags":{"description":"Het oorlogsmonument in Borculo (gemeente Berkelland) is opgericht ter nagedachtenis aan 67 joden en twintig andere medeburgers die tijdens de bezettingsjaren door oorlogshandelingen zijn omgekomen.","historic":"memorial","inscription":"VOOR HEN DIE HUN LEVEN GAVEN","memorial":"war_memorial","name":"Oorlogsmonument Borculo"}},{"type":"node","id":6712165793,"lat":52.1150201,"lon":6.5238857,"tags":{"direction":"165","historic":"memorial","inscription":"Je Kies de beemden en 't geboomt.\nDaer 't versche water lieflik stroompt.\nDaer sitt'ik neer, om wat te rusten.\nOf ga al wand'lend mij verlusten\nEn sie, in vreugt mijns herten dan \nHet schoon gebouw des hemels an.\n(uit Buiten-Leven van Willem Sluiter)","material":"plastic","memorial":"plaque","start_date":"19-12-2015"}},{"type":"node","id":6712165794,"lat":52.1147292,"lon":6.5240834,"tags":{"direction":"245","historic":"memorial","inscription":"Daer hilt bi eerlik ende wale.\nBi den grave Reynoude\nVan Gelre, ene baniere van goude,\nDaer waren in drie coken root;Die heere daeraf bleef eerlikke doot\nIn weringe ende in groter daet.\nHet was den grave van Gelre quaet,\nDat hine achter hem liet.","material":"plastic","memorial":"plaque"}},{"type":"node","id":6712165795,"lat":52.11601,"lon":6.5233588,"tags":{"direction":"80","historic":"memorial","inscription":"Waer iemand duisent vreugden soek\nMijn vreugt is in dees' achter-hoek","material":"plastic","memorial":"plaque","start_date":"19-12-2015"}},{"type":"node","id":6712165796,"lat":52.1156085,"lon":6.5241671,"tags":{"direction":"70","historic":"memorial","inscription":"Lieve Hennie.\nAls je soms in latre tijden.\nDe album eens doorziet\nWil dan aan mij blijven denken.\nAls je deze letters ziet.\n'k Mocht eens ver van je af zijn\nOf rusten in het graf.\nBlijf dan aan mij denken.\nDie je deze letters gaf.","material":"plastic","memorial":"plaque"}},{"type":"node","id":6712165797,"lat":52.1151344,"lon":6.5232999,"tags":{"historic":"memorial","inscription":"Ter herinnering aan de stormramp van Borculo\n10 Augustus 1925\nOnthult op 10.08.1985\nDoor mevr.A. Simmelink-Wissink\nBeeldhouster: Maïte Duval","material":"bronze","memorial":"statue","name":"De Stormramp","start_date":"10-08-1985"}},{"type":"node","id":6712165798,"lat":52.1150938,"lon":6.5243597,"tags":{"direction":"335","historic":"memorial","inscription":"anno domini 1606•den•j•mariona\nden•z•brant•welirdededes\ndit hus____In gadesha/godt be___waret/vor___bre\nDOOR STORM VERWOEST OP 10 AUG 1925 EN HERBOUWD IN 1926 DOOR HET PROV:STEUNCOMITE","material":"wood","memorial":"plaque"}},{"type":"way","id":57682355,"nodes":[715103218,715122465,5616924826,715123998,715094085,715106228,12800555508,12800555509,12800555507,715116206,715114046,715103218],"tags":{"historic":"memorial","leisure":"park","name":"Vrijheidsbos Geesteren","source":"3dShapes","website":"https://www.vrijheidsbosgeesteren.nl"}},{"type":"way","id":262523282,"nodes":[2681892822,2681892731,2681892766,2681892719,8323786377,8323786376,2681892751,2681892893,2681892903,2681892934,2681893017,6712165796,2681892915,2681892914,2681892822],"tags":{"building":"synagogue","heritage":"2","heritage:operator":"rce","historic":"synagogue","name":"Synagoge Borculo","ref:bag":"1859100000802624","source":"BAG","source:date":"2021-01-14","start_date":"1877","website":"https://www.synagogeborculo.nl","wikidata":"Q2688554","wikipedia":"nl:Synagoge (Borc